Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:06.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:10.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The grave... It's shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:54.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:11.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"One of the Fairy Tail's 3 \NGrand Spells, Fairy Glitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is sealed here."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:16.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:22.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Words I Couldn't Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:31.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you... What the hell are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:37.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you already. Where is Mavis's grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:40.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We don't know, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The grave of the founding Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has something to do with the second test?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:52.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's something completely \Nidiotic, but I suppose I'll ask anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:56.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to become an S class wizard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're not letting you into Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I shouldn't have asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:02.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:06.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cats should keep their damn mouths shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I asking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a crap about \Nsome exam or S class...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop treating me like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that's \Ntreating us like idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That grave is sacred to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we did know where it \Nwas, we'd never tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sparkle of fairies...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Glitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said to be on par with Fairy Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:39.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of your guild's 3 Grand Spells, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I got no idea what \Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:43.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm being crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:50.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That sparkle is a merciless light that \Ncannot stand the presence of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want that magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:03.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... the son of Igneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... be grounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:10.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's running!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in this gravity? Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that spell is \Nsealed at Mavis's grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell me where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy sure hates to lose, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:44.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What {\i1}is{\i0} he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Makarov lying over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:54.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I should just ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you try laying a hand on Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:04:59.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay down and shut up, you brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I just crush you all right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do? What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:17.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:27.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:30.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want isn't some spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I got all this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I thought I might \Nfinally become an S class wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The last 12 years are riding on this exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,12 years ago, my mother died from an illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and I found out in her will \Nthat my father was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:18.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched for him, and \Nit led me to Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My father's name is Gildarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, what are you doing standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry back home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand there too long and your clothes \Nwill start smelling like booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't he realize who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed my chance to tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, squirt, you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to hang around here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:10.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, when will Gildarts be coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...one of Gildarts' fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The job he just headed out on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:23.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two, three days, a month... \NWho knows, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He'll be back before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and drink some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:37.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I waited for my father to return, \Nand visited again and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up joining Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The city split!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana, it's the one you've \Nbeen waiting for, Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:00.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You had to wait for two months, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:02.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Good work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:15.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a carrier pigeon with a note from \Nthe client expressing their thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great going, Gildarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got someone we want \Nto introduce to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our new recruit, Cana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat her nice now, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:30.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, didn't realize it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:40.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the little girl I met at \Nthe entrance last time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So, you joined the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nice having you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about this when \Nyou just got back and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, could you come upstairs for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? What kind of request is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father would only return occasionally...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, he'd head right out again on a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:06.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure grown, Cana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're going to miss the train again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The words I couldn't say back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:28.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They grew larger and larger inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:37.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned the tarot in order to \Npredict the days he would return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you learned how to tell fortunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana's fortunes are pretty spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:49.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then you should learn \Nmagic that uses cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Card Magic, huh? Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:55.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Card Magic? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:59.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I can't do magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:01.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything begins from a \Nheart that believes, Cana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:09.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune, faith, and prayer \Nare all a form of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:14.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles where only those who \Nbelieve can sense them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:21.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in the existence of magic, \Nand believe in your own power...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who naturally \Nbelieve in both can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:30.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:34.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I learned how to use Card Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I could learn how to use magic, \NI could get a little closer to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:48.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was popular with everyone, and \Nthe number one wizard in the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even be compared to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was always a shining star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:59.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without being able to say \Nthe truth, time passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:04.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and at some point I became \Nafraid to say the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:09.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The turning point was the S \NClass Wizard Advancement Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:26.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I passed the test, I would \Ntell my father the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:35.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I failed four years in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:41.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza and Mira, who entered the guild \Nafter me, passed one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just the leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:49.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never live up to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:53.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided this \Nwould be the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:57.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of quitting the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:07.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that if I fail this time, I \Nhave no right to be Gildarts' daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll quit the guild, and leave the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your partner, Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you quit the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:21.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm going to make \Nyou an S class wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:29.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help, help, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:35.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a card to let me know \Nif you're in trouble, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If this card starts flashing during the exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:41.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to rescue you no \Nmatter how far away I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:03.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell have I been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't have turned out like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:25.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never intended to betray my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:30.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:43.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I can't \Nbecome an S class wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I can't tell \Nmy father how I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:53.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how much... I want \Nto protect my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as long as everyone else is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:06.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if I'm \Nno longer in the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:08.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because no matter where I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:12.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,my heart will always be in the same place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:21.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me the power to protect the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...love this guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:59.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistakes are not shackles that \Nhalt one from stepping forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, they are that which \Nsustain and grow one's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:12.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you the Fairy Glitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Mavis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:18.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:26.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be my final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:32.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you big time for these past \N12 years, everyone at Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:51.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Lucy! I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Fairy Tail's 3 Grand \NSpells, Fairy Glitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:16:01.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this magic, I can defeat any enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:16.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't gonna hurt my friends anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:29.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:30.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:34.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:42.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Fairy Glitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:50.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy... I'm sorry I left you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:52.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any excuse for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:58.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just, believe me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can hit him with this \Nmagic, I can beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:05.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it at the grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:06.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:09.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She was at the grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put that aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me to beat this guy, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:23.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep his attention while I \Ngather up the magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:35.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one who can move \Nunder my power of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:47.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought the magic I was \Nsearching for would just show up in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:49.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Glitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:52.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be taking that spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:56.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those in our guild can use this magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:05.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you trace back the origins of magic, all \Nmagic first began with a single spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:10.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every type of magic originally \Ncame from just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've heard \Nthat somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:24.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who get close enough to the depths of \Nmagic are able to use every type of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you, instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:39.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can a little girl like you \Nactually use Fairy Glitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely difficult spell that \Ngathers and concentrates sunlight and moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way someone like you could use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:02.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll take good \Ncare of that magic for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so stupidly powerful... \NBut in this gravity even he...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:20.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:21.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way, trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:31.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use this magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:43.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather to me, O River of \NLight led by the Fairies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I'm a Fairy Tail wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:02.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's from the other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars themselves are shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:10.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine down! To wipe out the fangs of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:18.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Glitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible light!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the guild's 3 Grand Spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:37.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:43.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that Fairy Glitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:11.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how powerful the magic. If \Nthe user is worthless, this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still take that magic \Neven after I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:22.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have enough power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:26.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to fly today, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:34.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will fall down to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:10.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:12.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:14.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:21.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:24:00.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The big tree on this island is \Ncalled the Tenrou tree, I hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.35,0:24:03.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the island where Fairy Tail's \Nfounding master rests, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some kind of fairy tree, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.45,0:24:08.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a fairy of the founding \Nmaster will show up or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, I wanna fight it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, do you have anything in your \Nhead other than eat, sleep, and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Tenrou Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.09,0:24:19.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sneak into Lucy's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.76,0:24:20.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Play pranks on Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.90,0:24:21.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:24.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like this might go on a \Nwhile... Can you write it down?
